for the last few years California has been “home.” i found lasting recovery here and felt the person who was taken away by disorder finally return bit by bit. i got my inner light back and found so much happiness. eternally grateful to Rady’s, UCSD, my family, my friends, my support system, my cat and the California beaches. as nervous as i am to start a new journey in NYC, i’ve never been more ready ♥️
